data.description: Welcome to this charming M/I home, a true gem built in 2020, nestled on a spacious corner lot in the coveted west side of San Antonio. With its modern amenities and convenient location near Loop 1604 and Culebra Rd, this property offers the perfect blend of comfort and accessibility.  As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a well-thought-out floor plan that emphasizes both style and functionality. This home boasts three generously sized bedrooms, ensuring ample space for your family's needs. Additionally, there's a versatile flex/loft area, perfect for a home office, playroom, or even a cozy reading nook.  One of the highlights of this home is the generously sized backyard, providing an ideal setting for your gatherings and quality family time. Whether you envision barbecues, gardening, or simply relaxing in the sunshine, this space offers endless possibilities.  The heart of this home is the kitchen, equipped with stunning espresso 42-inch cabinetry and a gas cooking range. It's a haven for any home cook, with plenty of counter space and storage to bring your culinary creations to life. The open concept design seamlessly integrates the kitchen with the dining and living areas, making it easy to entertain guests or keep an eye on the family while preparing meals.  In addition to its modern features, this home also offers a cozy atmosphere that will make you feel right at home. Welcome Home!
